item.title: I tested positive for COVID, taking the week off
item.description:
I'm feeling ok! I have a fever and I'm chilly and my test was positive so I'm gonna get some rest for a few days. But don't worry about me! Myself or one of several clones will be back soon!

(The clones have a birthmark on the butt. Trust me, you don't want to check!)

See you soon, Fluffle!
